{"tid":1611519,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以借鑑武俠小說啲兩軍對戰策略","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T06:17:50.000Z","uid":186989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a84e9803a19f639fe12d7dc90884bcd49cbb509","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"好多武俠小說都有兩軍對決既場面，我地可能可以借鏡嚟提升戰鬥力！<br />\n<br />\n講戰術之前，切記<span style=\"color: red;\">驕兵必敗</span>；同埋一條友無論gear幾齊全（武功高強），一到近戰混戰都完全冇優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係部分我覺得可以參考既策略：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 以量取勝<br />\n經常轉場，等班狗跟唔上我地既節奏，<span style=\"color: red;\"> 班狗佈防唔切 </span> 就會出現示威者人數壓倒既優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n貫徹呢場運動既motto: BE WATER，但<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔係隨便散水</span>，一定要維持一定人數<br />\n<br />\n魔法、磚海...自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 小隊式孤狼攻勢<br />\n當班狗佈防完成/緩兵到左，防線明顯守得好緊，我地就應該轉換形式，分散係唔同路口 以小隊孤狼形式放魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n放完即閃，班狗追到上嚟拉人既機會好低，因為佢地要守住自己個陣同防線，唔會立亂衝前捉人（通常拉人都係大馬路一條大直路），否則到時就係佢地落單，我地可以做返上一個point以量取勝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇武係心態，街坊都可以開遮/做人牆掩護</span>"},{"pid":"d3a1115000238fb2f165342d905cb51d1e4e80cd","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:41:41.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"387ca248183bc1db26c5a40734ba7edf42fc0c2b","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:49:51.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"237e38fd4408379e8639ccff9e627e85efd654ff","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:13:53.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ba9f9fbfca91c3acdbf4ef3ae8a4b26d5a77aaf2","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:21:11.000Z","msg":"7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f91f451e19f6dcf4087fe7b261fc7c9bf60606","tid":1611519,"uid":43685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"d7b5588c1da4aa7530c9b09eaa46f7470492b60b","tid":1611519,"uid":186142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:38:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻阻你<br />\n唔好再指責所謂偽勇武 入嚟睇下小勇武點可以有大作為<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【實際行動戰術整合】正式宣佈下回合開始將會冇人被捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1611678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1611678</a>"},{"pid":"abd97b795951ed7e4109beae1a15ab9234094191","tid":1611519,"uid":186989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T06:17:50.000Z","msg":"5"}]}